body:
downloading the .so file and dropping it into my project didn't solve the problem and generated an error while building the project : 

    No implementation found for void package_name_tracking.ObjectTracker.initNative(int, int, boolean)   (tried Java_package_name_tracking_ObjectTracker_initNative and Java_package_name_tracking_ObjectTracker_initNative__IIZ)

I opened an issue about this providing more informations about the problem please @andrewharp  check it out it's [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/19384) .
